extendedInfo.description: Delta Dentalâs mobile app gives you access to dentist search, claims and coverage and your ID card right on your mobile device. You must enter your user name and password each time you access the secure portion of the app. No personal health information is ever stored on your device. For more details on security, our Privacy Policy can be viewed via a link on the Login page of the app.About Delta DentalSince 1954, Delta Dental has been working to improve oral health by emphasizing preventative care, because we believe that everyone deserves to enjoy a healthy smile. reviews.title: Love it
reviews.comment: Great application, I went out of town on vacation and my crown came off, I just utilized the app to locate a Delta Dentist.  I will also refer to my friends that are looking for individual dental INS, the cost is reasonable.
reviews.author: janice mitchell

reviews.title: Horrible
reviews.comment: App does basically nothing. It takes you to one single webpage which works better if you just use an internet browser. I really wish this app would include a digital ID card for my proof of insurance.
reviews.author: Casey McPhedran

reviews.title: Pretty worthless, only function is find a dentist
reviews.comment: If all you need is to find a network dentist, then this app should fulfill what you need.  That being said, it is pretty poorly constructed.  Graphics are flimsy, buttons are small, the \"find a dentist\" feature simply directs you to their website.  There are really no native features to this \"app\".  You will have better luck with their mobile website.
reviews.author: Adam Tillotson
